# Descriptions
department-CaesarLegion-description = Caesar's Legion is an autocratic, traditionalist, imperialist slave-owning society and totalitarian dictatorship, founded on concepts of the Roman Empire.
department-Raider-description =
    The Blood Hounds are disorganized but deadly gangs that live by the law of the strong.
    They raid, kill and subjugate the weak, turning the wasteland into their hunting grounds.
    They have no ideology except one rule: "Take what you want and show no mercy."
department-BrotherhoodWest-description =
    The Brotherhood of Steel in the west is a paramilitary technocratic organization,
    whose members live in bunkers, waiting for the moment of "ascension".
    Obsessed with technology of the past, they preserve it from the unworthy, considering themselves the last defenders of pre-war heritage.
